@node "Installation" "Installation"
@{b}INSTALLATION:@{ub}

               
                          
@{u}Manual method:@{uu}

    Copy the appropriate MiniPlayer program to your "MiniPlayer:" directory.
    Copy the "powerpacker.library" into your "LIBS:" directory.
    Copy the "medplayer.library" into your "LIBS:" directory.
    Copy the "PowerPatcher (PP)" program into your "C:" directory.
 
Write to user-startup C:PP 
     
@endnode

@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
@{b}REQUIREMENTS:@{ub}
@{u}MiniPlayer requirements is:@{uu}

 Amiga 1MB,1.3+ kickstart
  
@{u}Recommended is:@{uu}
 
 Amiga 2MB Chip+2MB Fast,Hard Disk,68020+ processor,kickstart 2.0+ 
@endnode

@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@{b}INTRODUCTION:@{ub}

  MiniPlayer is a simple and fast music player.  
  Read formats is: 
  THX,Protracker/Noisetracker/SoundTracker/other tracker,MED,IFF/RAW
  Program can decrunch PowerPacker file if in "C:" directory is a PP file.
  Program show true date and time if yo have a clock.
@endnode


